1
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't see anything, but...</i></font>

2
00:00:21,130 --> 00:00:23,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can sense it. 
The little guy's in trouble.</i></font>

3
00:00:30,230 --> 00:00:33,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was able to sense her tao then...</i></font>

4
00:00:34,470 --> 00:00:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>because my blood blurred 
my vision in one eye.</i></font>

5
00:00:38,730 --> 00:00:42,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because I couldn't see, 
I relied on my senses.</i></font>

6
00:00:45,490 --> 00:00:49,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I gouged out one. The other's blurry.</i></font>

7
00:00:50,090 --> 00:00:52,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well... I can't see a thing.</i></font>

8
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I can sense it clearly now.</i></font>

9
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are an incredible woman.</font>

10
00:01:09,770 --> 00:01:11,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have my thanks.</font>

11
00:01:11,660 --> 00:01:14,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is starting to get interesting!</font>

12
00:01:30,150 --> 00:01:31,110
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#2d1508">Hell's Paradise</font></font></b></font>

13
00:01:31,110 --> 00:01:36,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A faint flower was blooming 
unnoticed by anyone</i></font>

14
00:01:36,470 --> 00:01:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not a burning red, 
but flickering serenely in red</i></font>

15
00:01:41,470 --> 00:01:46,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've been pausing for a long time 
dragging my past at my feet</i></font>

16
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I break free from this ambivalence,</i></font>

17
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:52,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>will I be able to bloom by its side?</i></font>

18
00:01:52,830 --> 00:01:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The future is slipping away 
between my fingers</i></font>

19
00:01:55,470 --> 00:01:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What mistake did I make 
to pay this price?</i></font>

20
00:01:57,990 --> 00:02:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Always hurting myself</i></font>

21
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:08,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and hesitant even to a small joy</i></font>

22
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to stop now</i></font>

23
00:02:10,390 --> 00:02:12,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The flower just bloomed in dignity</i></font>

24
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and that was all I needed to be happy</i></font>

25
00:02:15,530 --> 00:02:20,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just wanted to protect this one flower</i></font>

26
00:02:20,650 --> 00:02:23,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wishing to be strong, I</i></font>

27
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:26,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>picked up the vulnerability 
I had once cast away</i></font>

28
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Can't break free from the ambivalence</i></font>

29
00:02:27,970 --> 00:02:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In ambivalence, I become myself</i></font>

30
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:33,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like rooting strongly into the soil</i></font>

31
00:02:33,870 --> 00:02:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>like swaying ephemerally to the wind</i></font>

32
00:02:36,420 --> 00:02:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm slowly loosening myself to bloom</i></font>

33
00:02:39,510 --> 00:02:42,720
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40">Hell's Paradise</font></b></font>

34
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:52,530
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>Chrysanthemum and Peach</b></font>

35
00:02:52,190 --> 00:02:58,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In a world without war, conquering it 
with a sword is a pipe dream.</i></font>

36
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that didn't stop me.</i></font>

37
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I sought to become the fastest, 
sharpest, and strongest swordsman.</i></font>

38
00:03:08,420 --> 00:03:11,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wanted only one thing.</i></font>

39
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:15,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To cut down every powerful warrior...</i></font>

40
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and live forever by carving 
my name into history.</i></font>

41
00:03:36,460 --> 00:03:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you so strong, old man?</font>

42
00:03:42,490 --> 00:03:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're skinnier and 
slower than me, so how?</font>

43
00:03:46,740 --> 00:03:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tetsunosuke, you're too greedy.</font>

44
00:03:50,580 --> 00:03:53,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to be everything 
because you're young.</font>

45
00:03:53,670 --> 00:03:58,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thicker, harder, hotter, faster.</font>

46
00:03:58,890 --> 00:04:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've lost focus.</font>

47
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:05,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not everything a person eats 
becomes part of them.</font>

48
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eat too much, and it'll 
pass right through you.</font>

49
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine while you're young, 
but cut back once you get older.</font>

50
00:04:13,650 --> 00:04:18,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cast off everything you can 
and look closely at what's left.</font>

51
00:04:18,010 --> 00:04:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll find everything within that.</font>

52
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:23,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't go wider. Go deeper.</font>

53
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flip it on its side, and it's the same.</font>

54
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never get what you're saying.</font>

55
00:04:32,170 --> 00:04:36,170
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b></b>{\an8}<font color="#555557"><font size="25">Sakataya Rice</font></font></font>

56
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:36,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back then, I didn't understand 
my master's words.</i></font>

57
00:04:36,170 --> 00:04:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bastard!</font>

58
00:04:37,420 --> 00:04:38,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll pay for this!</font>

59
00:04:38,590 --> 00:04:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

60
00:04:43,710 --> 00:04:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I traveled around the country.</i></font>

61
00:04:48,490 --> 00:04:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I understand now.</i></font>

62
00:04:51,460 --> 00:04:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The more you accumulate, 
the harder it becomes to see yourself.</i></font>

63
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The less you have...</i></font>

64
00:05:11,490 --> 00:05:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the better you can see.</i></font>

65
00:05:17,220 --> 00:05:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've made me even stronger.</font>

66
00:05:20,380 --> 00:05:22,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

67
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:23,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

68
00:05:23,620 --> 00:05:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that won't kill me!</font>

69
00:05:26,110 --> 00:05:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll spend my whole life!</font>

70
00:05:28,100 --> 00:05:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An eternity!</font>

71
00:05:30,150 --> 00:05:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forever and ever!</font>

72
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:35,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cutting you again and again!</font>

73
00:05:36,110 --> 00:05:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How romantic!</font>

74
00:05:42,350 --> 00:05:44,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's determined.</i></font>

75
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if this becomes 
a battle of attrition...</i></font>

76
00:05:49,540 --> 00:05:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>we'll lose.</i></font>

77
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if he can see her tao, he can't 
kill her without the hindering effect.</i></font>

78
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#e4f0dd">Wood</font></font>

79
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#e6acaf">Fire</font></font>

80
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f3e0d4">Earth</font></font>

81
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#e5dec7">Metal</font></font>

82
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#dce9f5">Water</font></font>

83
00:05:57,460 --> 00:05:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tao Fa's attribute is wood.</i></font>

84
00:06:00,420 --> 00:06:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My metal attribute could kill her,</i></font>

85
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:05,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I can't use tao well enough 
to be effective.</i></font>

86
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If we wait too long, 
Gantetsusai will die of blood loss.</i></font>

87
00:06:10,050 --> 00:06:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What should we do?</i></font>

88
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Restoration is a flow 
that supports yours.</font>

89
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hindrance is one that halts it.</font>

90
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:25,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing? Move, Little-emon!</font>

91
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this what you're into?</font>

92
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hindrance kills Tensen because it 
prevents their tanden from regenerating!</font>

93
00:06:32,020 --> 00:06:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words,</font>

94
00:06:33,250 --> 00:06:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as long as I'm touching her tanden 
immediately after it's destroyed,</font>

95
00:06:36,710 --> 00:06:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the effect is the same!</font>

96
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:41,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cut her, Tamiya Gantetsusai!</font>

97
00:06:41,490 --> 00:06:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

98
00:06:42,230 --> 00:06:44,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Naturally, you must cut as close 
as possible without cutting me.</font>

99
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would be child's play for an Asaemon.</font>

100
00:06:46,890 --> 00:06:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it too difficult for you, Blade Dragon?</font>

101
00:06:52,810 --> 00:06:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it!</font>

102
00:06:58,670 --> 00:07:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Honestly, it's nearly impossible 
to be precise with these eyes.</i></font>

103
00:07:03,370 --> 00:07:05,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At this rate, 
I'll cut the little guy, too.</i></font>

104
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:16,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cast off everything you can 
and look closely at what's left.</font>

105
00:07:16,490 --> 00:07:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll find everything within that.</font>

106
00:07:32,430 --> 00:07:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

107
00:07:33,850 --> 00:07:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go, Little-emon. Child's play.</font>

108
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:40,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ju Fa...</font>

109
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:47,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Without hindrance, this never ends.</i></font>

110
00:07:47,460 --> 00:07:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But we don't have time for this.</i></font>

111
00:07:51,330 --> 00:07:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll have to use that.</i></font>

112
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do it, Brother.</font>

113
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's kill them together.</font>

114
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

115
00:08:03,380 --> 00:08:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you really think you'd 
survive turning against us?</font>

116
00:08:08,530 --> 00:08:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You fools don't consider consequences.</font>

117
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Consequences?</font>

118
00:08:12,850 --> 00:08:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter the riff-raff 
ahead or behind me,</font>

119
00:08:15,330 --> 00:08:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just crush whoever gets in my way.</font>

120
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I count on him to stand at my side.</font>

121
00:08:19,490 --> 00:08:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all I need.</font>

122
00:08:22,890 --> 00:08:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may be livestock, 
but I can agree with that.</font>

123
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:31,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two is enough.</font>

124
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ju Fa, help me!</font>

125
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:48,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Tao Fa.</font>

126
00:08:48,890 --> 00:08:51,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got heated and left you by yourself.</font>

127
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and I belong together.</font>

128
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:06,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll crush them together.</font>

129
00:09:07,270 --> 00:09:11,020
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#03020f"><font size="25">Hell's Paradise</font></font></b></font>

130
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:19,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ju Fa and Tao Fa, you are two as one.</font>

131
00:09:21,650 --> 00:09:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're all family,</font>

132
00:09:25,190 --> 00:09:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you're special.</font>

133
00:09:29,340 --> 00:09:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I more or less understood.</i></font>

134
00:09:37,500 --> 00:09:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nobody else fears the Soshin or doshi.</i></font>

135
00:09:42,740 --> 00:09:45,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They take their studies seriously, too.</i></font>

136
00:09:46,860 --> 00:09:51,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But Tao Fa fears the Soshin, 
and I don't really like studying.</i></font>

137
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nobody really cares 
if one of us gets hurt,</i></font>

138
00:10:00,870 --> 00:10:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>probably because they don't die.</i></font>

139
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I don't like seeing 
Tao Fa get hurt at all.</i></font>

140
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's probably because you 
have someone you care about.</font>

141
00:10:22,810 --> 00:10:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We feel our own pain, but we can 
only imagine the pain of another.</font>

142
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you imagine it 
because you care about them.</font>

143
00:10:33,710 --> 00:10:36,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Imagination is the source 
of anxiety and kindness.</font>

144
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:40,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just harder to notice 
with bodies like ours.</font>

145
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ju Fa, we're all playing over here.</font>

146
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:45,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tao Fa.</font>

147
00:10:47,230 --> 00:10:48,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we go?</font>

148
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have plenty of time.</font>

149
00:10:51,060 --> 00:10:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can take our time studying together.</font>

150
00:10:56,100 --> 00:10:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The first change was Rien.</i></font>

151
00:10:59,850 --> 00:11:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They are Hoko. Prototype Tensen.</font>

152
00:11:05,180 --> 00:11:07,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were sent to live outside the castle.</font>

153
00:11:08,140 --> 00:11:11,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use them to replenish your lost tao.</font>

154
00:11:11,390 --> 00:11:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Replenish?</font>

155
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will begin your proper training now.</font>

156
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:20,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the reason you were created.</font>

157
00:11:21,290 --> 00:11:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ran will study doin.</font>

158
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:24,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mu Dan will study shuten.</font>

159
00:11:24,620 --> 00:11:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gui Fa will study shuitsu.</font>

160
00:11:26,330 --> 00:11:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zhu Jin will study taisoku.</font>

161
00:11:29,210 --> 00:11:30,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And...</font>

162
00:11:39,110 --> 00:11:41,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ju Fa and Tao Fa will study bochu jutsu.</font>

163
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the reason I raised you together.</font>

164
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know this is sudden, 
but it can't be helped.</font>

165
00:11:48,940 --> 00:11:53,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll focus on your studies 
and teach each other.</font>

166
00:11:53,890 --> 00:11:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The kindness disappeared from Rien.</i></font>

167
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:04,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to use the Hoko.</font>

168
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help imagining how they feel.</font>

169
00:12:18,060 --> 00:12:19,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neither do I, Tao Fa.</font>

170
00:12:19,910 --> 00:12:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not much, but let's use fruit 
to replenish our tao.</font>

171
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

172
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad I was paired with you, Ju Fa.</font>

173
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Several years later, 
Mei vanished from the castle.</i></font>

174
00:12:37,700 --> 00:12:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't know why.</i></font>

175
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But significantly, nobody seemed to care.</i></font>

176
00:12:45,050 --> 00:12:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our training became more intense,</i></font>

177
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and our sense of reality 
became even more distorted.</i></font>

178
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:57,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. I'm here.</font>

179
00:12:59,260 --> 00:13:01,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I must protect Tao Fa's smile.</i></font>

180
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:08,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A hundred years passed, and the animals 
we brought from the mainland died out.</i></font>

181
00:13:09,070 --> 00:13:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our training continued.</i></font>

182
00:13:11,690 --> 00:13:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A hundred more years passed, 
and the Hoko village fell into ruin.</i></font>

183
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:18,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our training continued.</i></font>

184
00:13:19,910 --> 00:13:22,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long are we going to keep doing this?</font>

185
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soon the Hoko will be gone, 
and we'll run out of crops.</font>

186
00:13:25,940 --> 00:13:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are Rien and 
the grandmaster thinking?</font>

187
00:13:28,710 --> 00:13:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They must have a plan.</font>

188
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can bring in sources of tao 
from the outside.</font>

189
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The outside? You mean humans?</font>

190
00:13:38,300 --> 00:13:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Obviously.</font>

191
00:13:40,010 --> 00:13:45,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't like that, eventually 
we'll run out of tao and die.</font>

192
00:13:45,090 --> 00:13:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're not truly immortal.</font>

193
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, I doubt we'll 
achieve perfect immortality</font>

194
00:13:53,470 --> 00:13:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">no matter how much we train.</font>

195
00:14:00,410 --> 00:14:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean our training and 
Tao Fa's suffering was pointless?</font>

196
00:14:11,890 --> 00:14:15,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How can they smile?</i></font>

197
00:14:15,990 --> 00:14:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Have they truly lost their minds?</i></font>

198
00:14:18,910 --> 00:14:22,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Have they grown accustomed to the 
endless training and lost their minds?</i></font>

199
00:14:23,030 --> 00:14:24,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Or is it me?</i></font>

200
00:14:24,860 --> 00:14:27,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are Tao Fa and I the crazy ones?</i></font>

201
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I must protect Tao Fa's smile.</i></font>

202
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:42,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that, Tao Fa?</font>

203
00:14:43,590 --> 00:14:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chum. It's for attracting 
humans from the outside.</font>

204
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:54,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the grandmaster's homeland, 
they send flowers with invitations.</font>

205
00:14:54,100 --> 00:14:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that perfect?</font>

206
00:14:56,170 --> 00:14:58,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we do it enough times,</font>

207
00:14:58,320 --> 00:15:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">some humans who find it strange 
might come to investigate.</font>

208
00:15:02,710 --> 00:15:05,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kaijin won't attack it if we 
launch it through the sluice gate.</font>

209
00:15:05,910 --> 00:15:08,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ocean currents 
will carry it to Wakoku.</font>

210
00:15:09,350 --> 00:15:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to use the Hoko.</font>

211
00:15:12,010 --> 00:15:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help imagining how they feel.</font>

212
00:15:15,310 --> 00:15:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tao Fa, are you okay with this?</font>

213
00:15:30,620 --> 00:15:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Totally.</font>

214
00:15:34,180 --> 00:15:35,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that weird?</font>

215
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, of course not.</font>

216
00:15:56,890 --> 00:16:00,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Humans are like the Hoko. 
Less than livestock.</font>

217
00:16:01,470 --> 00:16:03,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're ours to use.</font>

218
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're not crazy.</i></font>

219
00:16:17,270 --> 00:16:20,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's this world that's crazy.</i></font>

220
00:16:33,860 --> 00:16:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everything besides us is crazy.</i></font>

221
00:16:38,180 --> 00:16:41,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Livestock, livestock.</font>

222
00:16:42,210 --> 00:16:44,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's their Kishikai transformation?</font>

223
00:16:44,940 --> 00:16:46,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They combined.</font>

224
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feathers—no, wings?</font>

225
00:16:49,470 --> 00:16:52,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, it can't be easy 
for them to move indoors.</font>

226
00:16:59,040 --> 00:17:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't do anything like this!</font>

227
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you say?</font>

228
00:17:02,460 --> 00:17:03,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother!</font>

229
00:17:11,890 --> 00:17:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm amazed it can fly with those wings.</font>

230
00:17:13,910 --> 00:17:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I agree. Structurally, 
it should be impossible.</font>

231
00:17:17,470 --> 00:17:21,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Twisted and unnatural, 
yet somehow seductive.</font>

232
00:17:21,150 --> 00:17:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their appearance is like love itself.</font>

233
00:17:26,220 --> 00:17:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're struggling 
after your betrayal, Big Brother.</font>

234
00:17:29,730 --> 00:17:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After that monster, you're next, old man.</font>

235
00:17:32,340 --> 00:17:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not letting you beat me to it.</font>

236
00:17:35,360 --> 00:17:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

237
00:17:36,330 --> 00:17:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're bleeding too much. 
Let me tend your wounds.</font>

238
00:17:38,940 --> 00:17:41,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't have time for that.</font>

239
00:17:41,060 --> 00:17:45,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I kill that monster, 
my name will go down in history.</font>

240
00:17:45,340 --> 00:17:47,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you'll die!</font>

241
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm okay with that.</font>

242
00:18:08,460 --> 00:18:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gantetsusai! Hey!</font>

243
00:18:11,290 --> 00:18:13,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are those fluffy spores causing this?</i></font>

244
00:18:17,870 --> 00:18:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

245
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:22,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take cover. Touching 
the spores is dangerous.</font>

246
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is bad.</font>

247
00:18:30,030 --> 00:18:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They keep falling.</font>

248
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:33,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother!</font>

249
00:18:34,490 --> 00:18:37,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know, but don't stop me now.</font>

250
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

251
00:18:40,660 --> 00:18:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As long as I maintain my sense of self, 
I can control this power.</i></font>

252
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:03,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As I thought, my metal tao 
is effective against Tao Fa's wood.</i></font>

253
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#e4f0dd">Wood</font></font>

254
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#e6acaf">Fire</font></font>

255
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f3e0d4">Earth</font></font>

256
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#e5dec7">Metal</font></font>

257
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#dce9f5">Water</font></font>

258
00:19:03,450 --> 00:19:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I can destroy her tanden, she'll die.</i></font>

259
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

260
00:19:35,210 --> 00:19:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother!</font>

261
00:19:38,050 --> 00:19:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're both enormous and quick.</i></font>

262
00:19:40,620 --> 00:19:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And most of all, they've got two tanden.</i></font>

263
00:19:44,520 --> 00:19:47,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where'd all your bluster go, Big Brother?</font>

264
00:19:47,230 --> 00:19:48,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up.</font>

265
00:19:48,050 --> 00:19:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother! Brother, Brother, Brother!</font>

266
00:19:50,850 --> 00:19:53,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, okay. Calm down, all of you.</font>

267
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No single one of us can kill that monster.</font>

268
00:19:57,990 --> 00:20:00,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We may not like it, but 
we have to work together.</font>

269
00:20:00,090 --> 00:20:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Work with him? You're joking.</font>

270
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want you anyway. You're injured.</font>

271
00:20:04,850 --> 00:20:06,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're one rude brat.</font>

272
00:20:06,810 --> 00:20:08,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your brother's indebted to me 
for teaching him, you know.</font>

273
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's not a brat! 
And I don't owe you anything!</font>

274
00:20:11,090 --> 00:20:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You heard him.</font>

275
00:20:12,230 --> 00:20:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do I need to punish both of you?</font>

276
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up, idiot.</font>

277
00:20:24,830 --> 00:20:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our current enemy is that monster.</font>

278
00:20:28,990 --> 00:20:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to kill 
each other, do it after.</font>

279
00:20:33,590 --> 00:20:36,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you hold me back, I'll kill you.</font>

280
00:20:36,660 --> 00:20:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right back at you.</font>

281
00:20:39,390 --> 00:20:41,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Let's do this.</font>

282
00:20:41,580 --> 00:20:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still treating your wounds.</font>

283
00:20:43,610 --> 00:20:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm amazed you stuck around this guy.</font>

284
00:20:46,190 --> 00:20:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one who told me 
to wait for you.</font>

285
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, then.</font>

286
00:20:52,430 --> 00:20:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go kill a monster.</font>

287
00:21:08,100 --> 00:21:14,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>On the other side, even today</i></font>

288
00:21:14,230 --> 00:21:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone is unraveling, 
yet they still stand</i></font>

289
00:21:20,190 --> 00:21:26,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A stab to the chest, this loneliness</i></font>

290
00:21:26,100 --> 00:21:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Points and lines, 
breaking off and vanishing</i></font>

291
00:21:31,930 --> 00:21:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My shattered mask</i></font>

292
00:21:34,830 --> 00:21:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's more than I can bear</i></font>

293
00:21:37,910 --> 00:21:40,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I must keep on living</i></font>

294
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tomorrow awaits to greet me</i></font>

295
00:21:45,690 --> 00:21:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's endless</i></font>

296
00:21:48,650 --> 00:21:51,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And so fragile</i></font>

297
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it better to believe 
hearts don't exist at all?</i></font>

298
00:21:57,450 --> 00:22:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Radiant and soft</i></font>

299
00:22:03,010 --> 00:22:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was the hand</i></font>

300
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I squeezed back on that day</i></font>

301
00:22:28,850 --> 00:22:34,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How much farther until we reach that 
Horai place the doshi thing mentioned?</font>

302
00:22:34,340 --> 00:22:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roughly eight ri. 
We'll be there before tomorrow.</font>

303
00:22:36,940 --> 00:22:37,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

304
00:22:37,860 --> 00:22:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this not a bit reckless?</font>

305
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say shinobi can run 40 ri in a day,</font>

306
00:22:43,750 --> 00:22:46,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we're samurai. Without horses...</font>

307
00:22:48,050 --> 00:22:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we'll use the horse whistle.</font>

308
00:22:51,620 --> 00:22:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Horse whistle?</font>

309
00:22:52,710 --> 00:22:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. You're not serious, are you?</font>

310
00:22:56,220 --> 00:22:57,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I am.</font>

311
00:22:57,220 --> 00:22:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The doshi told us how to use it 
during the interrogation.</font>

312
00:22:59,940 --> 00:23:03,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've completely lost your mind. Don't—</font>

313
00:23:03,430 --> 00:23:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shugen-sama, the genin searching 
the area have returned.</font>

314
00:23:07,610 --> 00:23:11,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They recovered what we believe are 
the personal effects of the expeditioners.</font>

315
00:23:11,140 --> 00:23:12,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you take a look at them?</font>

316
00:23:15,590 --> 00:23:18,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tenza... Genji...</font>

317
00:23:18,840 --> 00:23:21,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be...</font>

318
00:23:21,410 --> 00:23:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother... Brother Genji!</font>

319
00:23:25,110 --> 00:23:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Judging by the state of the bodies, 
some were killed by criminals.</font>

320
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have no time to waste.</font>

321
00:23:34,630 --> 00:23:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We must travel to Horai as quickly 
as possible and find our companions.</font>

322
00:23:37,580 --> 00:23:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will kill the sages and the criminals.</font>

323
00:23:42,860 --> 00:23:44,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, Shugen-sama...</font>

324
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:49,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the cave.</font>

325
00:23:50,770 --> 00:23:52,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please use the horse whistle.</font>

326
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that whistle for?</font>

327
00:23:54,830 --> 00:23:56,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you remember?</font>

328
00:23:56,620 --> 00:23:59,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's for controlling monsters.</font>

329
00:24:02,190 --> 00:24:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The monsters live inside that cave.</font>

330
00:24:07,250 --> 00:24:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't be serious.</font>

331
00:24:08,260 --> 00:24:10,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm deadly serious.</font>

332
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I said...</font>

333
00:24:12,800 --> 00:24:15,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shugen's lost his mind.</font>

334
00:24:21,020 --> 00:24:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm on my way.</font>

